    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is totally ready for its next adventure. I'd love to see it go to a great home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I've loved it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 34500.0,
