    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This driver-focused machine delivers an exceptional mechanical experience, featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a crisp six-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a refined double-wishbone suspension geometry and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip and corner-exit traction. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a fresh set of high-performance staggered-width tires. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited road use, the powertrain exhibits robust compression and seamless power delivery across the entire rev range. A true purist\u2019s spec, optimized for tactile feedback and balanced weight distribution.",
      "price": 38500.0,
