    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Deep Charcoal Metallic that still holds a deep shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway commuting. The body lines remain straight and the doors shut with a solid, factory feel. Inside, the cabin features premium black leather upholstery that has been kept smoke-free; while there is some light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the seats remain supportive and free of any rips or stains. Every interior feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust and dependable. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires offer plenty of tread for the seasons ahead. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
